        {
            "title": "一艘法國所有的貨櫃船駛出霍爾木茲海峽",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"via Bloomberg\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"728\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/uLEceUSUyTlD3TLpUmYFaw--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTcyOA--/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/44b006926e6f0275db300a2d98438f40\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">via Bloomberg</figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><br/></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> 一艘顯示為法國所有的貨櫃船駛出了<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"霍爾木茲海峽\",\"ySubModuleName\":\"anchor_text\",\"yHasCommerce\":false}' data-ylk=\"slk:霍爾木茲海峽;sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link;itc:0\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/tag/霍爾木茲海峽\">霍爾木茲海峽</a>，這似乎是自戰爭導致這條水道近乎完全封鎖以來，與西歐有關的船隻首次通過海峽。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">據船舶追蹤數據，名為CMA CGM Kribi的船舶於當地時間周四下午從杜拜附近海域駛往伊朗，並發出信號表明其為法國所有。該船緊貼伊朗海岸航行，穿過格什姆島和拉拉克島之間的海峽，並公開廣播其航程。周五上午，該船發出信號顯示已抵達馬斯喀特附近海域。兩名知情人士也表示，該船已穿過海峽。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-f08a8e8d-cbfe-32b8-a7d7-86abe495e8a6-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"CMA CGM Kribi船駛出霍爾木茲海峽來源： 彭博\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"728\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/NId0esw66xRrAdPOcx03NQ--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTcyOA--/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/564a6c41d8c60348872b8813ae79a0ea\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">CMA CGM Kribi船駛出霍爾木茲海峽來源： 彭博</figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">這艘懸掛馬耳他國旗的船隻屬於全球第三大貨櫃航運公司達飛集團。該公司和法國外交部均不予評論，法國財政部未回應尋求評論的請求。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">推薦閱讀：霍爾木茲海峽追蹤：與德黑蘭和中國有關船隻沿北部航線通過</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題French-Owned Container Ship Exits Hormuz in First Since Iran War</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">--聯合報導 Tara Patel.</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"bloomberg.com\"}' data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2026 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
